《'''無境之獸'''》（{{lang-en|''Beasts of No Nation''}}）是一部2015年[[凱瑞·福永|凱瑞·福永]]编剧、执导和拍摄的美国战争剧情片，改编自2005年出版的由[[尼日利亚|尼日利亚]]裔美国籍作家[[乌佐丁玛·伊维拉|乌佐丁玛·伊维拉]]（Uzodinma Iweala）所写的同名小说。[[伊卓瑞斯·艾巴|伊卓瑞斯·艾巴]]、[[阿巴漢·阿塔|阿巴漢·阿塔]]、[[Ama_K._Abebrese|Ama K. Abebrese]]、Grace Nortey、David Dontoh和Opeyemi Fagbohungbe主演。影片入选[[第72届威尼斯影展|第72届威尼斯影展]]主竞赛片<ref name="InComp">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2015-full-list-1201486791/|title=Venice Film Festival: Lido Lineup Builds Awards Season Buzz – Full List|accessdate=29 July 2015|work=Deadline|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808192428/http://deadline.com/2015/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2015-full-list-1201486791/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/venice-fest-reveals-robust-lineup-featuring-hollywood-stars-and-international-auteurs-1201551960/|title=Venice Fest Reveals Robust Lineup Featuring Hollywood Stars and International Auteurs|accessdate=29 July 2015|work=Variety|archive-date=2017-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625075544/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/venice-fest-reveals-robust-lineup-featuring-hollywood-stars-and-international-auteurs-1201551960/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，男主角Abraham Attah赢得最佳新演员奖<ref name="winners">{{cite web|title=LIVE: The winners of the 72nd Venice Film Festival|url=http://cineuropa.org/nw.aspx?t=newsdetail&did=298479|accessdate=12 September 2015|archive-date=2017-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007221238/http://cineuropa.org/nw.aspx?t=newsdetail&did=298479|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它也进入2015年[[多伦多影展|多伦多影展]]特别展映单元<ref name="ScreenDaily">{{cite web |url=http://www.screendaily.com/toronto-world-premieres-for-trumbo-demolition-the-program/5090990.article?blocktitle=LATEST-FILM-NEWS&contentID=40562# |title=Toronto to open with 'Demolition'; world premieres for 'Trumbo', 'The Program' |date=28 July 2015 |accessdate=28 July 2015 |work=ScreenDaily |archive-date=2015-07-29 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20150729193951/http://www.screendaily.com/toronto-world-premieres-for-trumbo-demolition-the-program/5090990.article?blocktitle=LATEST-FILM-NEWS&contentID=40562%23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年10月16日美国有限上映<ref name="deadline.com">{{cite news|work=Deadline|date=July 2015|title=Netflix feature films|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/netflix-feature-films-paul-reubens-adam-sandler-judd-apatow-idris-elba-pee-wee-herman-1201471559/|accessdate=2015-10-27|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203201732/http://deadline.com/2015/07/netflix-feature-films-paul-reubens-adam-sandler-judd-apatow-idris-elba-pee-wee-herman-1201471559/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==剧情==

小男孩阿古的家人在战争中丧生，于是他一个人逃进深山老林，并遇上一群[[游击队|游击队]]。游击队首领是一个凶狠粗暴的指挥官，他带领一群士兵四处征战报仇杀戮。为了活命，阿古加入游击队并渐渐被训练成一个杀人机器。

