==制作==
2014年6月5日，影片在[[加纳|加纳]]取景开拍。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mycelebrityandi.com/pix-from-idris-elbas-beast-of-no-nation-movie-shoot-in-ghana/|publisher=mycelebrityandi.com|title=Pix from Idris Elba’s Beast of no Nation Movie Shoot in Ghana|accessdate=29 June 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923085524/http://www.mycelebrityandi.com/pix-from-idris-elbas-beast-of-no-nation-movie-shoot-in-ghana/|archive-date=2015-09-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Yamato|first1=Jen|title=First Look Photo: Idris Elba In Cary Fukunaga’s ‘Beasts Of No Nation’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/06/idris-elba-beasts-of-no-nation-cary-fukunaga-first-photo/|accessdate=29 June 2014|publisher=deadline.com|date=27 June 2014|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709221927/http://www.deadline.com/2014/06/idris-elba-beasts-of-no-nation-cary-fukunaga-first-photo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>小男孩阿塔哈是名加纳人。由于当地环境恶劣，导演凱瑞·福永在六个月的拍摄中染上了[[寄生虫病|寄生虫病]]，导致他本人消瘦了20斤；而男主角伊德里斯·艾尔巴差点摔下悬崖，摄影师在拍摄过程中脚部受伤。

== 反响 ==
